Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.11,0:01:32.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:89110,92196}Was its owner using this boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.19,0:01:37.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:92196,97702}That's because I found its leash in this boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.70,0:01:40.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:97702,100872}When I read the name written on it,\Nit replied immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.49,0:01:43.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:102498,103833}Isn't it, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.08,0:01:46.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:105084,106252}You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.71,0:01:50.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:108713,110298}Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.29,0:01:51.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:110298,111758}Oh, is it you, John?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.75,0:01:54.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:111758,114719}Don't you know who owns that boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.71,0:01:55.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:114719,115803}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.80,0:01:57.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:115803,117347}Ah, that one…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.34,0:02:01.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:117347,121476}That was here just a few days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.47,0:02:03.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:121476,123978}Maybe it has no owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.22,0:02:06.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:125229,126522}I knew when I looked at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.19,0:02:13.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:127190,133071}The boat's rope was cut off, indicating\Nthat the owner was running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.07,0:02:13.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:133071,133988}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.98,0:02:16.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:133988,136491}Perhaps not to run away,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.49,0:02:19.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:136491,139035}I think the rope it teared by itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.16,0:02:21.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:140161,141829}Maybe so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.82,0:02:26.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:141829,146626}In fact I don't know\Nthe answer to your question.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.46,0:02:40.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:156469,160014}Where did this boat come from?\NI wish I could find the answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.93,0:02:44.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:160932,164018}Tell me, where did you came from?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.39,0:02:50.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:168398,170692}Is it wise to move it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:53.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170692,173945}But we must find the owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.94,0:02:54.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:173945,174821}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:56.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174821,176114}Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:03.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:180451,183913}Because, if we know where it came from
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:07.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:184622,187750}we may find the mother of Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:08.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:187750,188960}Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.96,0:03:12.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:188960,192505}I understand, if you find the owner\Nyou will give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:14.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:192505,194298}We have no other choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:15.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:194298,195967}We have no other choice…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:22.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:195967,202598}True, if Lassie lives with its mother,\Nit will live happily ever after.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:26.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204016,206477}Maybe you are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:28.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:207770,208896}It's an airplane!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.93,0:03:33.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:209939,213359}The delivery goods that were\Nin my house are on the plane now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:34.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:213359,214777}My father is a contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:41.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:217780,221784}I remembered, I met you for the first time\Nwhen I saw the plane flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.87,0:03:47.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:223870,227498}If the plane wasn't there,\NI would't meet Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:04.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:242096,244223}This is the school road!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:06.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:244807,246684}That bridge we always see!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.76,0:04:09.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:247769,249395}What?! John and Colin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.39,0:04:11.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:249395,251189}Where did you get this boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:16.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254859,256319}Isn't it great?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.31,0:04:19.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:256319,259197}We are going to Lassie's mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:20.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:259197,260031}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:22.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:260031,262158}Have you found the owner of the puppy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:23.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:262158,263785}Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:27.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:264786,267705}But I'm sure we'll find Lassie's mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:31.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:267705,271918}Wait for me! I'll go with you!\NWait! Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:34.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:272627,274295}There is the backyard of the houses!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:35.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:274295,275338}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:37.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:275338,277799}First time I see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:41.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:279175,281219}I saw him, I saw him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:44.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:283221,284013}John!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:48.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:286098,288559}Mr. Curry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.23,0:04:54.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:292230,294440}She's so beautiful, teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:05:01.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:298361,301614}The village looks quite different by the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:02.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:301614,302990}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:12.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:311123,312416}Dr. Hopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,0:05:18.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:313626,318339}Hello, you're Carraclough's son, isn't it?\NThat's a good boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:19.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:318339,319507}Yes, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:23.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:320716,323719}This remainds me… what was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:29.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:324595,329016}I remembered, I saw a puppy on board\Nof this boat two or three days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:31.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:329016,331644}Dr. Hopper, have you seen it before?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:35.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:331644,335690}Yes, it came on this river.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.69,0:05:36.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:335690,336357}John!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.35,0:05:37.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:336357,337066}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.56,0:05:40.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:337567,340069}Doctor, thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.06,0:05:45.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:340069,345992}Hey, it's important not to tell\Nyour mother that you saw me here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:57.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:355042,357211}What is it? You are a coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:06.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:365303,366888}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:38.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:397293,398669}We crossed a long distance…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:40.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:398669,400504}How long we'll continue this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:42.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:401714,402798}Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.59,0:06:45.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:403591,405259}It's a steamer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.31,0:07:00.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418314,420358}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:03.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:422026,423569}Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:06.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:425363,426489}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:10.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:428783,430743}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,0:07:18.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:436916,438417}This is dangerous, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.41,0:07:21.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:438417,441712}If you cross this road, you will be crushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:26.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:445007,446467}What is it with this wheel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:27.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446467,447551}John!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:28.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:447551,448469}Hey John!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:31.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:449720,451597}Look here! This rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:35.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452264,455601}It's the same rope as on the boat,\Nit's cut in the same shape!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:38.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:456227,458104}Well that means…?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:41.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:458104,461399}Look, the two ropes are exactly the samel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.39,0:07:44.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:461399,464485}So Lassie was coming from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.98,0:07:49.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:464986,469490}We are going to find your mother soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:51.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:470616,471993}We finally found her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:08:01.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:478332,481252}Hey, it's so annoying, so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:05.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:481252,485381}You two! Children, you are making\Nnoise around other people's houses!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:09.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:486340,489969}Hey! It's my boat that I lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:10.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:489969,490886}Eh… eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:17.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:493389,497727}Well, we came to look for\Nthe owner of this boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:19.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:497727,499687}It's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:20.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:499687,500855}Whatever…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:22.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:502023,502690}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.02,0:08:24.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:503024,504316}What's with this puppy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:28.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:504316,508195}Sorry for this… sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:30.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508195,510156}Isn't that Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:31.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510156,511157}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.15,0:08:33.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:512158,513534}This means…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:37.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:514452,517747}Uncle, do you know anything about Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:40.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:517747,520541}Of course I know, because it's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:41.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:520541,521625}What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:44.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:522668,524628}Do you want to say this again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:48.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:524628,528049}No, I understand, I will return it immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:49.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:528883,529884}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:08:51.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:530176,531135}What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:55.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531886,535389}It stayed with me for a while
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:58.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:535389,538809}after it almost crumbled\Nunder the feet of the sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:02.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:538809,542313}So please let me say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:03.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:542313,543773}Hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:07.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:544315,547109}I will give it some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:08.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:547109,548652}When you finish it, bring it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:19.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:556744,559580}This is great, Lassie, we've found your owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:22.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:560873,562291}Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:25.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:562666,565294}Give your mother a lot of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:26.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:565294,566796}Take care of yourself, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:30.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:568005,570299}I won't forget you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:36.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:572885,576055}Come on, now go to your mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:45.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:582645,585481}Hey go! Don't you want to meet your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.36,0:09:49.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:589360,589944}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:53.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:591403,593364}Lassie, not that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:02.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:599578,602665}I understand, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:05.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:602665,605626}I will do it immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:07.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605626,607169}Oh, the child!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:09.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:607169,609839}Don't play here, move right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:11.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:610464,611924}This is not a place to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:14.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:612716,614969}I understand, I'll do it right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:19.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:614969,619265}The water level must rise quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:24.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:620307,624603}Shut up, our steam pump is not…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:29.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:626438,629441}Damn, I have no time for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.40,0:10:37.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:635406,637116}Hey kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:41.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:637575,641120}Come here and help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:49.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:644123,649503}Listen Lassie, this is just a wheel,\Nso you have to go to your owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.50,0:10:50.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:649503,650212}Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.21,0:10:53.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:650212,653174}So pull more and work hard, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:11:00.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:656552,660181}What is the matter? Can't you move it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:03.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:662766,663934}What do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:06.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:663934,666770}Close the gate to raise the water level!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:11.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:667146,671775}This side must be closed\Nwhen this ship comes…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:15.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:672276,675738}We must send the high water\Nto the opposite side!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:17.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:675738,677323}What is the matter? Have you closed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:20.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:678532,680326}It's closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:29.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:686290,689627}But, why do you do that, Colin?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:34.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:690544,694131}I did this because the uncle\Nasked me to do so, to use my force.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.13,0:11:35.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:694131,695507}What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:38.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:696342,698886}Kid, have you called this puppy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:59.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:713275,719990}And as it looks, they can leave now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:04.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:722493,724161}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:06.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:724161,726247}I still want to rest more…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:08.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:727164,728499}You can't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.99,0:12:10.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:728999,730668}Are you satisfied with this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:17.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:733212,737383}And don't you think of coming here again,\Ngo away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:21.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:738467,741553}Uncle, will you use it for guarding?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:24.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:741553,744348}Don't ask about things that don't concern you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.34,0:12:26.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:744348,746642}Do you live here alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:27.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:746642,747476}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.47,0:12:30.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:747476,750813}Don't you have a family other than this puppy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.81,0:12:33.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:750813,753148}What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:36.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:754441,756443}If there is no other choice for us…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.90,0:12:42.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:759905,762283}Well get here immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:44.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:762283,764285}If you'll do bad things, I'll eat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:50.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:765953,770040}You must open the rest of the gates quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:51.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:770040,771917}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:22.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:798068,802281}I'm sure that man knows\Nhow to behave with the poor Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:23.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:802281,803574}I hope so, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.65,0:13:26.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:804658,806327}I found it, I should tell him so!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:27.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:806327,807369}John?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:34.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:811540,814376}What is it? You are the child\Nwho came earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:35.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:814376,815627}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:36.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:815627,816920}Sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:41.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:817463,821133}Lassie drinks milk from a child's bottle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.13,0:13:42.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:821133,822259}So…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.13,0:13:44.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:823135,824178}So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.17,0:13:48.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:825179,828557}But you try to train it to eat from the dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:49.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:828557,829600}So… sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.60,0:13:51.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:829600,831852}You, uncle, will you…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:54.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:832561,834980}How long will you keep bothering me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:59.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:836565,839777}I have no time to train it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:02.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:839777,842613}If it doesn't drink milk\Nby its own, is it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:05.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:842613,845491}Is it over? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:08.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:845491,848243}I don't know, how will I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.87,0:14:11.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:849870,851538}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:16.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:852289,856168}Well, this world is not that easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.16,0:14:17.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:856168,857211}John…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:17.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:857211,857753}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:20.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:858295,860255}Come on, let 's go back…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.46,0:14:25.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:864468,865511}Eh…?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:30.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:866678,870474}Listen, John, let's go back…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:32.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:870474,872476}But that sounds fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:36.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:873602,876271}Ah, it worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.83,0:14:56.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:893831,896458}Don't look at my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:09.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:905843,909388}What is it, why do you look\Nat other people's houses?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.38,0:15:11.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:909388,911723}But I was surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:14.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:911723,914893}That an amazing machine like this\Ncould be found in someone's house!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:17.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:914893,917521}Would you let me look at it a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:19.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:917521,919481}I will not!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:21.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:919481,921400}I told you not to look!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:22.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:921400,922317}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:23.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:922317,923193}What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.19,0:15:24.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:923193,924695}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.94,0:15:26.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:924945,926488}Don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:31.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:929867,931827}It's not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.82,0:15:33.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:931827,933287}Not here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:38.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:935664,938041}You have to leave immediately, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:41.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:938625,941670}Sorry, is there a house for the dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.67,0:15:42.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:941670,942421}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.42,0:15:44.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:942421,944840}A dog house? There is no such thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:48.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:944840,948844}Hey? No house for the dog?\NWhere did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:51.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:949178,951138}What do you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.13,0:15:53.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:951138,953307}I don't have time for your likes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:15:57.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:956185,957561}Get away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.56,0:15:59.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:957561,959062}I said no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:02.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:959062,962649}What would you do if a ship\Npassed by and didn't notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.64,0:16:05.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:962649,965444}Another question? Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.52,0:16:09.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:966528,969573}Hey, listen to me, uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:12.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:970199,972284}I want to ask you something else!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:14.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:972284,974286}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:15.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:974286,975829}It's important!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:18.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:976747,978582}John, enough, let 's go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:21.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:978582,981418}But… it's really important!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:26.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983003,986507}I will answer only one question!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:27.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:986507,987633}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.67,0:16:33.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:988675,993138}Excuse me, what do you have\Nto eat for today, uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:36.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:995015,996892}How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:38.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:996892,998852}Is this what you wanted to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.85,0:16:40.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:998852,1000145}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.89,0:16:43.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002898,1003941}It's canned food!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:44.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1003941,1004983}Canned food?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:48.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004983,1008695}Yes, today canned food\Nand every day canned food!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:51.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1008695,1011782}I don't have time to cook\Nso my food is just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:55.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1013283,1015786}Hey, this is great…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.32,0:17:00.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1016328,1020916}It's not like it's good, there's no food to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:07.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022292,1027297}Kid, why are you interested by my food?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.83,0:17:13.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027839,1033303}If you don't have food to eat,\Nyou may have to eat Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:14.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1033303,1034513}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:18.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1034513,1038559}If you think I'll really eat the puppy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:19.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038559,1039977}I can't eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.52,0:17:23.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041520,1043689}Maybe this is the truth but…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:28.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043689,1048986}But I don't see Lassie's mother here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:29.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048986,1049903}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:32.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1049903,1052281}You don't see Lassie's mother here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:34.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052281,1054449}Where is Lassie's mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.44,0:17:37.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1054449,1057494}I didn't eat it, because I don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.91,0:17:42.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057911,1062124}Uncle! I don't see it! Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:47.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062124,1067546}I want to find Lassie's mother\Nand bring it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:50.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1067546,1070090}Why isn't it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.09,0:17:52.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070090,1072801}The puppy's mother is really not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:55.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072801,1075095}Yes, I looked around the place thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:59.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1075095,1079516}He's a liar! He's not the owner of Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.60,0:18:04.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081602,1084104}I'm not a liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:05.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1084104,1085439}I hate lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:10.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087899,1090736}It's because of that driver!\NThe driver…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:14.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090736,1094156}Driver! Yes, that wheel…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:18.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1096867,1098368}Do you know that, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:22.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098368,1102539}No, but it was strange of Lassie\Nto smell that wheel…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.20,0:18:28.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1104207,1108462}A few days ago there was\Na car on this road with a flat tire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:32.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108754,1112466}He is said he was coming from a foreign\Ncountry and was accompanied by a Collie dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.13,0:18:37.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1113133,1117888}When the driver fix his car,\Nthis puppy fled away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:39.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117888,1119264}He couldn't find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:42.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119973,1122934}The port was far away and\Nhe couldn't stay any longer
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.93,0:18:44.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1122934,1124978}so he decided to leave it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.97,0:18:49.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124978,1129858}He also asked me to take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.85,0:18:53.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129858,1133612}You understand, this puppy belongs to me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:56.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1133612,1136365}He left it under my care,\Nso I have no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:19:00.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1138575,1140786}Stop with that bark!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:04.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1140786,1144164}You can't take care of it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:07.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1144164,1147501}You have to promise me\Nthat you will take good care of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.87,0:19:09.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147876,1149670}Stupid, in such a place…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:13.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152214,1153507}What are you doing, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:17.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153507,1157386}I thought it would grow better with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:20.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157386,1160847}but if I left Lassie with you, it would die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.84,0:19:22.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160847,1162516}For sure…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.51,0:19:26.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162516,1166728}I mean you wanted to take care of it\Ninstead of someone like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:27.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1166728,1167854}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:29.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1167854,1169856}No? Don't lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:31.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1169856,1171525}I'm not a liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.52,0:19:32.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1171525,1172943}And now stay there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.48,0:19:37.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1174486,1177030}You want to take care of it\Nuntil it grows up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:38.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177030,1178407}I won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.57,0:19:41.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1179574,1181493}You are a honest kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:46.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184663,1186581}He made me go and come with no reason…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:48.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1186581,1188500}John, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:53.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1191545,1193588}Well, don't come here again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:57.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1193588,1197676}I want to take care of the puppy!\NGo, liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.42,0:20:01.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1198427,1201263}I can't do that before you promise me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.26,0:20:02.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1201263,1202723}Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:06.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205100,1206351}Oh! John!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:13.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1210981,1213817}I can't leave you now, grab it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:19.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1213817,1219531}No, I won't do that before you promise me\Nto take good care of Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.78,0:20:21.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219781,1221700}This time is not appropriate for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.70,0:20:25.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221700,1225287}I won't bother you again if you promise me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:27.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1225287,1227539}Insubordination will only make matters worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.53,0:20:29.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227539,1229708}Don't try to contradict me anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.96,0:20:35.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1232961,1235881}Look, it's a ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:38.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236298,1238884}If you continue your stubbornness,\Nyou will regret it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:45.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1242262,1245056}I understand, I promise you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:20:59.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1258195,1259237}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.19,0:21:03.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1260197,1263533}This uncle lives alone, so stay with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:06.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1263533,1266244}Hm!\NAs if it would understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.07,0:21:09.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1268079,1269289}Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:10.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1269289,1270832}It's yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.83,0:21:14.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1270832,1274461}But I brought it to you\Nbecause you are its owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:18.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1274461,1278048}It's true that I have made you a promise…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:22.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1278048,1282344}But if you are so proud of it\Nthen you can take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.17,0:21:26.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1283178,1286348}It's annoying, it likes you\Nso I'll leave it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.81,0:21:35.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1291812,1295607}Come to the hut again, all three of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.60,0:21:39.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1295607,1299319}You will taste some sea-food!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.31,0:21:40.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1299319,1300529}Be sure to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.52,0:21:42.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1300529,1302864}Yes, we'll certainly come!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.24,0:21:47.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1304241,1307160}Now Lassie, let's go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.16,0:21:50.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1307160,1310705}You'll be getting hot milk, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.17,0:22:01.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1319172,1321216}{\i1}Tomorrow is my mother's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.21,0:22:04.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1321216,1324678}{\i1}But my father lost his salary.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.67,0:22:07.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1324678,1327806}{\i1}He can't bring any gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.80,0:22:10.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1327806,1330976}{\i1}Lassie, you'll find it with your smell!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.97,0:22:13.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1330976,1333353}{\i1}Next episode:\N"My Father's Salary".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.35,0:22:14.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1333353,1334688}{\i1}Be sure to watch!
